        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
            Restudent was founded in 2020 with the mission to bring delicious and high-quality food to our community. Our journey began with a passion for cooking and a love for sharing great meals with friends and family.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Quality: We use only the freshest ingredients in all our dishes.</li>
            <li>Service: Our staff is dedicated to providing the best dining experience.</li>
            <li>Community: We believe in giving back and supporting local initiatives.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
        <p>
            Our team is comprised of experienced chefs, friendly waitstaff, and dedicated management, all working together to make your visit memorable.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Menu</h2>
        <p>
            From classic favorites to unique creations, our menu offers something for everyone. Whether you’re in the mood for a hearty meal or a light snack, you’ll find plenty of options to satisfy your cravings.
        </p>

        <h2>Join Us</h2>
        <p>
            We invite you to visit us and experience the warm, welcoming atmosphere of Restudent. Whether you’re dining in, taking out, or catering a special event, we look forward to serving you.
